{"tid":137901,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港地理] 究竟點解西貢叫西貢 東涌叫東涌","createTime":"2017-02-28T07:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T12:59:51.000Z","uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bfd77d8a90b5f3ab791d94d38a1eadeca258b69","tid":137901,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"明明西貢喺香港嘅東邊<br />\n東涌喺香港嘅西邊<br />\n點睇都叫東貢同西涌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 淨係識分上下左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47de80bd21ffa809d2c5f33209bc57a5c608b570","tid":137901,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"搵人解答我呀唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20fe297f66f8478d5bb839c47c2a96f769bc11e","tid":137901,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"香港西貢同越南西貢有咩關聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f328c36690a5fd524a0b89f9270a11538217a998","tid":137901,"uid":41742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T09:13:54.000Z","msg":"google 幫到你"},{"pid":"ff7a36f593804d8a21788afc5af722ef32f6970c","tid":137901,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:38:24.000Z","msg":"靜係識分上下左右 點解唔係 左/右貢，左/右涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"821a2437920e02e79dffe1650549bb34eb7c1c12","tid":137901,"uid":16058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靜係識分上下左右 點解唔係 左/右貢，左/右涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b203bee7095e82c9aa10da962bfd7616efa3bc3","tid":137901,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"真心一問，會唔會以前香港個版圖唔係咁，所以西貢既響個時香港西邊，所以叫西貢<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"78dc6c1a0f04c88fa5d652df249dff8573186e0c","tid":137901,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"「西貢」一名，大約在明初才出現。從明成祖永樂三年至宣宗宣德八年，明朝廷曾派遣鄭和七次「下西洋」。在這七次「下西洋」後，不少東西亞、中東沿海、東非等國家也向明朝進行朝貢和貿易。而在當時，西貢便是西來朝貢船隻停泊的港口。久而久之，這裡就稱為「西貢」，有「西方來貢」的意思。"},{"pid":"9ed9e42738dca613fcfbe967a642763e11898bab","tid":137901,"uid":51978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:58:26.000Z","msg":"東涌原稱東西涌，首見於明萬曆《粵大記》等古籍，因東西兩邊各有一河涌流入海中。清道光《廣東海防匯覽》把「東西涌」分別標記為「東涌口」和「西涌口」兩個地方，最後東邊的鄉鎮發展較好，人們統稱整個地區為「東涌」。"},{"pid":"a33ab11eadec49c4b8e5229d4629a6a7f37a885c","tid":137901,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東涌原稱東西涌，首見於明萬曆《粵大記》等古籍，因東西兩邊各有一河涌流入海中。清道光《廣東海防匯覽》把「東西涌」分別標記為「東涌口」和「西涌口」兩個地方，最後東邊的鄉鎮發展較好，人們統稱整個地區為「東涌」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}